com.gotenna.sdk

Class GTEventNotifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gotenna.sdk.GTEventNotifier

  • public class GTEventNotifier
extends java.lang.Object
    A singleton that is used to log when specific events occur, and send a broadcast that other classes can listen for. Created on 2/6/15.
